# Phase 32 Walkthrough — Multi-Chain Split Payments

**Build status:** ✅ Clean (exit code 0, all routes compiled)  
**Commit:** `5ce0aac` — feat: Phase 32 - Multi-chain split payments (Base/Solana)

---

## What Was Built

### 1. [contracts/VibeStreamSplitter.sol](file:///C:/GOLive/contracts/VibeStreamSplitter.sol) — Base Splitter Contract
Production Solidity smart contract deployed on Base (and any EVM chain).
- **`tipETH(creator)`** — atomic 75/25 ETH split in one transaction
- **`tipUSDC(creator, amount)`** — atomic USDC split via ERC20 transferFrom  
- **48-hour timelock** on platform wallet changes (prevents immediate damage if key is compromised)
- **`recoverERC20()`** for emergency stuck token recovery (owner only)
- **No custody** — funds flow directly from fan wallet to creator + platform

### 2. [lib/constants.ts](file:///C:/GOLive/lib/constants.ts) — Secure Wallet Config
All wallet addresses now read from **Vercel environment variables**, not source code.

```
NEXT_PUBLIC_PLATFORM_WALLET_EVM=0x5b9C3D6e92F4e6A7fD03cBC1f60da3De002BC1a8
NEXT_PUBLIC_PLATFORM_WALLET_SOLANA=DDztsJc2RmC2m2DvKFoB3ActexVkdzHZqYdMd3UXY6ft
NEXT_PUBLIC_VIBESTREAM_SPLITTER_CONTRACT= (fill after deployment)
NEXT_PUBLIC_PRIVY_APP_ID= (fill from dashboard.privy.io)
```

### 3. [components/VibeStreamPrivyProvider.tsx](file:///C:/GOLive/components/VibeStreamPrivyProvider.tsx) — Auto-Wallet at Signup
Every new user gets a non-custodial **Base + Solana embedded wallet** generated at their first login. No seed phrase required. Powered by [Privy](https://privy.io).

### 4. [lib/useAutoSaveWallet.ts](file:///C:/GOLive/lib/useAutoSaveWallet.ts) — Wallet Auto-Save Hook
After Privy generates the embedded wallet, this hook automatically saves the wallet address to the creator's Supabase profile — so they have a payout address from Day 1.

### 5. [components/TipButton.tsx](file:///C:/GOLive/components/TipButton.tsx) — Production Payment Modal
- **Base (ETH)** → calls deployed `tipETH()` on [VibeStreamSplitter.sol](file:///C:/GOLive/contracts/VibeStreamSplitter.sol) (single tx, atomic split)
- **Base (USDC)** → calls `approve()` then `tipUSDC()` (2 steps, but atomic split in contract)
- **Solana (SOL)** → single atomic transaction with 2 SystemProgram.transfer instructions
- **Solana (USDC)** → single atomic SPL token transfer split (creator + platform ATAs)
- Correct amount presets per asset (USDC: $1/$5/$20 — ETH: 0.001/0.005/0.02 — SOL: 0.1/0.5/2)
- Transaction explorer link after success
- Full ARIA accessibility

### 6. [scripts/phase32-wallets.sql](file:///C:/GOLive/scripts/phase32-wallets.sql) — Database Migration

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Run this in your Supabase SQL editor to activate wallet storage and tip tracking:**
> `https://supabase.com/dashboard/project/puhrqtwakabyvagnvcch/sql`

```sql
ALTER TABLE profiles ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS solana_wallet_address TEXT;
ALTER TABLE profiles ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS wallet_address TEXT;
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS tip_transactions (...);
```

