## Security Model Summary

```
Fan pays $5 USDC
    → approve(VibeStreamSplitter, $5)
    → tipUSDC(creatorAddress, $5)
        → $3.75 → Creator wallet (direct)
        → $1.25 → Platform wallet (direct)
        → 0 funds held by contract
```
- Contract never holds funds
- Platform wallet is in env vars (not source code)
- Wallet changes require 48h timelock
- Privy wallet keys secured via TEE + key sharding
